      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 16:59:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选后投资者撤出中国 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/investors-yank-cash-from-china-etfs-following-trump-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利加剧了加征更严厉关税的风险，而刺激措施未能让投资者相信中国能够安然度过即将到来的风暴，基金经理上周从购买中国股票的交易所交易基金中撤出了现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/investors-yank-cash-from-china-etfs-following-trump-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 16:58:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
